title: 01/04/21 - HOUR 1 - Washington Football Team & Peter King
itunes:title: 01/04/21 - HOUR 1 - Washington Football Team & Peter King
description:
In hour 1 of the Dan Patrick Show the guys recap the up & down year of the Washington Football Team. Being the NFC East champs, cutting 1st round draft pick in Dwayne Haskins. Peter King joins the show to talk about Doug Peterson questionable call to bench players late in game, Tom Brady's year in Tampa Bay and more.
